name: Pickle Jar yvBOOST-ETH
description: This token represents a Sushiswap strategy for ETH-yvBOOST. yvBOOST is the upgraded version of yveCRV, which compounds the weekly reward from CRV automatically. SUSHI is sold for more ETH-yvBOOST LP.
